&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; devaru ( kannada : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ದೇವರು ) is a 1971 indian kannada language drama film written by shivam and directed by siddalingaiah . it stars rajkumar , m. v. rajamma and bharathi in the lead roles . the film was released under jain movies banner and produced by chandulal jain . h. r. bhargava worked as associate director , m. s. rajashekar as assistant director and g. k. venkatesh was the soundtrack and score composer . the dialogues and lyrics were written by chi . udaya shankar .